[SN]TITLE[SN]
Pentland Firth search for missing diver

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Three lifeboats and the coastguard helicopter are searching in the Pentland Firth for a diver, reported missing from a dive boat off Burwick in Orkney.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The alarm was raised just before five thirty this afternoon.
Coastguard search teams from Hoy and St Margarets Hope and four commercial vessels in the area are also assisting in the operation.
The search is being co-ordinated by coastguards.
